{"tid":2007678,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共匪：建議公務員凍薪   港共：按機制考慮 黨衛除外","createTime":"2020-05-08T12:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T15:40:59.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ac54f0a6c10731c227545a673414000f52fb8d","tid":2007678,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"華員會籲公務員凍薪 局方：行會按機制全盤考慮<br />\n08.05.2020 20:22<br />\n<br />\n華員會呼籲全體公務員在今個財政年度凍薪。華員會發聲明指，對於今年度公務員薪酬調整，政府要審時度勢，通盤考慮，指凍薪是公務員對社會經濟下行的分擔，同時兼顧減少對中、低級公務員的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局回應指，行政長官會同行政會議，會按既定薪酬調整機制，在全盤考慮各項相關因素後，決定年度公務員薪酬調整，當中包括職方對薪酬調整的要求，待2020年薪酬趨勢調查結果公布後，公務員事務局局長會安排與職方代表會面，聽取他們的要求，並向行政長官會同行政會議反映他們的意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286146&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286146%26csid%3D261_341&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQIBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=440ee02b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286146&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"575ffef1321c64e406a3d5a1e4a662207362b4ee","tid":2007678,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"華員會出賣藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f0e57c3cc461183871932d5383698e00ab1ab0","tid":2007678,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:53:16.000Z","msg":"咩凍薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扣啦屌<br />\n大把人糧都無得出<br />\n共度時姦啦"},{"pid":"08d0c8d92e42d045bac3d0119cda8268bdc3f86a","tid":2007678,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"華員會食屎啦！"},{"pid":"7c70aaa0d52e3f9d6d671e6746ccb78596c11936","tid":2007678,"uid":293543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"華員會竟然咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/sca